lead_paragraph: Defending champion Agnieszka Radwanska made light work of Olympic gold medallist Monica Puig, beating the Puerto Rican 6-2 6-3 in the quarter-finals of the Pan Pacific Open in Tokyo on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Tennis-Radwanska Closes In on Third Pan Pacific Open Title
